</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Clerics-Peridots and You</span><hr size=1> As Eve I tend to to keep everyone but me with Symbol on.<br>
I don't symbol Eve cause well it just takes mana I would <br>
rather have to heal in the next 5 minutes. <br>
<br>
The main problem with this comes when not everyone carries <br>
peridots.  So one person in the group wants to suck up the <br>
cost for the whole group so they can have a chance at a <br>
random gem drop.  When I am in OS all the rare gems are <br>
randomed Eve gets the regular ones to cover the cost of <br>
dots.  On nights that we get lots of gems and I know the<br>
dots have been covered for that day. We then just random <br>
all the gems.<br>
<br>
Everyone would have to carry a personal supply of Peridots<br>
to make this work.  I just don't see that coming to pass <br>
in the future. Most people don't carry chr gear and have the <br>
faction fixed to up high enough so that peridots don't cost <br>
them an arm and a leg most clerics do we have too.  A stack<br>
costs about 230pp. <br>
<br>
We master loot and we split for between 30 and 50 pp after<br>
3 hours in OS. <br>
<br>
I keep everyone with symbol. Even Druids Even Bards.<br>
Bards make thier own agro even if they aren't mezzing. <br>
Bards also tend to die fast so I would rather have a couple<br>
more seconds to get my heal to them so I symbol bards.<br>
Druids are usually snaring which also can get the druid <br>
spanked.<br>
<br>
That said I do symbol in order of risk and as mana allows.<br>
Tanks, Pullers and Enchanter/Bard/Necro (Whatever we have<br>
as a mezzer) Get first symbols. Then casters/druids. After<br>
that depending on the danger of the camp I sometimes <br>
symbol myself.  <br>
<br>
I think the system is fair as my regular group tends to play.<br>
To me this just seems like someones reason to whine about <br>
loot. In dangerous zones you take risks and give a bit to <br>
cover the level of danger.  I couldn't afford to pay for the <br>
symbols on my own. If I didn't have the gems to cover the <br>
cost I wouldn't be able to symbol at all.  I am not getting <br>
rich quick on gem drops.<br>
<br>
